                         │ Subscription Renewed   │
                         └────────────────────────┘



                    ──────────────────────────────────────
                          ACCOUNT DELETION FLOW
                    ──────────────────────────────────────


                     User Deletes Business Account
                                  │
                                  ▼
                    ┌───────────────────────────────┐
                    │ Soft Delete (2 Months)        │
                    │                               │
                    │ All Data Preserved            │
